00:13:09,289 --> 00:13:12,124
<font color="yellow">- Kami baik-baik saja.
- Baiklah.</font>

186
00:13:13,460 --> 00:13:14,835
<font color="yellow">- Maaf soal api itu.
- Tak apa.</font>

187
00:13:15,003 --> 00:13:16,587
<font color="yellow">Tidak perlu minta maaf.</font>

188
00:13:18,089 --> 00:13:19,798
<font color="yellow">Selamat malam, semuanya.</font>

189
00:13:20,842 --> 00:13:22,468
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih.</font>

190
00:13:22,635 --> 00:13:24,803
<font color="yellow">Aku menghargai kerja sama
kalian.</font>

191
00:13:34,564 --> 00:13:37,065
<font color="yellow">Apa kau memikirkan Daryl Dixon?</font>

192
00:13:37,233 --> 00:13:39,943
<font color="yellow">Dia takkan senang mendengar
kakaknya ditinggal.</font>

193
00:13:40,111 --> 00:13:43,155
<font color="yellow">Aku akan memberitahunya.
Kujatuhkan kuncinya. Salahku.</font>

194
00:13:43,323 --> 00:13:45,073
<font color="yellow">Aku yang memborgolnya.
Harusnya itu salahku.</font>

195
00:13:45,241 --> 00:13:46,742
<font color="yellow">Kawan-kawan,
ini bukan kompetisi.</font>

196
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:48,577
<font color="yellow">Aku tak bermaksud
ikut campur...</font>

197
00:13:48,745 --> 00:13:51,651
<font color="yellow">...tapi mungkin akan terdengar
lebih baik jika kulit putih yang bicara.</font>

198
00:13:53,541 --> 00:13:55,167
<font color="yellow">Kulakukan yang seharusnya.</font>

199
00:13:55,335 --> 00:13:57,503
<font color="yellow">Aku tak akan bersembunyi
darinya.</font>

200
00:13:57,670 --> 00:14:00,631
<font color="yellow">- Kita bisa berbohong.
- Atau katakan yang sebenarnya.</font>

201
00:14:00,798 --> 00:14:03,050
<font color="yellow">Merle tak bisa dikendalikan.</font>

202
00:14:03,218 --> 00:14:06,136
<font color="yellow">Sesuatu harus dilakukan atau
dia akan membuat kami terbunuh.</font>

203
00:14:07,263 --> 00:14:09,097
<font color="yellow">Suamimu melakukan hal
yang diperlukan.</font>

204
00:14:09,265 --> 00:14:10,682
<font color="yellow">Dan jika Merle ditinggal...</font>

205
00:14:10,850 --> 00:14:12,851
<font color="yellow">...itu bukan salah siapa-siapa
namun salahnya sendiri.</font>

206
00:14:13,019 --> 00:14:15,270
<font color="yellow">Dan itu yang akan kita
katakan pada Daryl?</font>

207
00:14:17,148 --> 00:14:21,777
<font color="yellow">Aku tak melihat ada diskusi masuk
akal yang dipetik dari itu, bukan?</font>

208
00:14:24,572 --> 00:14:26,114
<font color="yellow">Asal tahu saja...</font>

209
00:14:27,283 --> 00:14:30,702
<font color="yellow">...kita akan sibuk menenangkannya
saat dia kembali dari perburuan.</font>

210
00:14:32,539 --> 00:14:35,832
<font color="yellow">Aku takut dan aku lari.</font>

211
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:38,210
<font color="yellow">- Aku tidak malu akan hal itu.
- Kita semua takut.</font>

212
00:14:38,378 --> 00:14:40,837
<font color="yellow">Kita semua lari.
Apa maksudmu?</font>

213
00:14:41,005 --> 00:14:43,090
<font color="yellow">Aku berhenti cukup lama
untuk merantai pintu itu.</font>

214
00:14:45,218 --> 00:14:46,677
<font color="yellow">Tangganya sempit.</font>

215
00:14:46,844 --> 00:14:51,223
<font color="yellow">Mungkin sekelompok zombie bisa
naik bersamaan.</font>

216
00:14:51,391 --> 00:14:53,642
<font color="yellow">Namun itu tak cukup
untuk mendobraknya.</font>

217
00:14:53,810 --> 00:14:55,894
<font color="yellow">Tidak untuk rantai
dan gembok itu.</font>

218
00:14:58,064 --> 00:15:01,692
<font color="yellow">Maksudku, Dixon masih hidup...</font>

219
00:15:01,859 --> 00:15:04,778
<font color="yellow">...dan dia masih di atas sana,
terborgol di atap itu.</font>

220
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:07,739
<font color="yellow">Dia tanggung jawab kita.</font>

221
00:15:20,753 --> 00:15:24,339
<font color="yellow">Ayah menemukanmu, bukan?</font>

222
00:15:26,926 --> 00:15:28,093
<font color="yellow">Aku menyayangimu, Ayah.</font>

223
00:15:30,763 --> 00:15:32,764
<font color="yellow">Ayah juga menyayangimu, Carl.</font>

224
00:16:12,055 --> 00:16:14,139
<font color="yellow">Aku menemukan kalian berdua.</font>

225
00:16:15,308 --> 00:16:16,933
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

226
00:16:20,521 --> 00:16:22,189
<font color="yellow">Aku tahu aku akan
menemukan kalian.</font>

227
00:16:23,816 --> 00:16:26,485
<font color="yellow">Kau kini mulai sedikit sombong.</font>

228
00:16:26,653 --> 00:16:28,945
<font color="yellow">Tidak, aku tahu.</font>

229
00:16:30,657 --> 00:16:33,659
<font color="yellow">Saat memasuki rumah kita,
kudapati rumah dalam keadaan kosong.</font>

230
00:16:33,826 --> 00:16:35,661
<font color="yellow">- Kalian berdua tak ada.
- Maafkan aku.</font>

231
00:16:35,828 --> 00:16:38,914
<font color="yellow">Aku tahu kau masih hidup.</font>

232
00:16:40,833 --> 00:16:42,834
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana bisa?</font>

233
00:16:44,504 --> 00:16:46,880
<font color="yellow">Foto-foto tak ada
di tempatnya.</font>

234
00:16:47,048 --> 00:16:49,174
<font color="yellow">Semua album keluarga kita.</font>

235
00:17:12,532 --> 00:17:14,366
<font color="yellow">Sudah kubilang.</font>

236
00:17:14,534 --> 00:17:17,035
<font color="yellow">Sekarang kau menjadi sombong.</font>

237
00:17:17,203 --> 00:17:18,704
<font color="yellow">Sangat sombong.</font>

238
00:17:32,385 --> 00:17:34,386
<font color="yellow">Foto ini pantas berada
di sini.</font>

239
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:43,603
<font color="yellow">Sayang, aku benar-benar berpikir
takkan pernah bertemu kau lagi.</font>

240
00:17:48,025 --> 00:17:49,943
<font color="yellow">Maafkan aku...</font>

241
00:17:51,404 --> 00:17:53,071
<font color="yellow">...atas segalanya.</font>

242
00:17:55,908 --> 00:18:00,162
<font color="yellow">Aku merasa saat kau di RS,
aku hanya...</font>

243
00:18:00,329 --> 00:18:02,080
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin mencabut semuanya.</font>

244
00:18:02,248 --> 00:18:04,666
<font color="yellow">Kemarahan dan masa sulit.</font>

245
00:18:04,834 --> 00:18:07,335
<font color="yellow">Tapi kesalahan...</font>

246
00:18:10,757 --> 00:18:12,924
<font color="yellow">Mungkin kita mendapat
kesempatan kedua.</font>

247
00:18:13,092 --> 00:18:15,260
<font color="yellow">Tidak banyak orang
memperoleh hal itu.</font>

248
00:18:32,320 --> 00:18:34,867
<font color="yellow">Aku bertanya-tanya ke mana
hilangnya cincin ini.</font>

249
00:18:36,115 --> 00:18:38,575
<font color="yellow">Kau menginginkannya lagi?</font>

250
00:18:40,620 --> 00:18:42,496
<font color="yellow">Tentu saja.</font>

251
00:19:28,292 --> 00:19:30,293
<font color="yellow">Dia takkan bangun.</font>

252
00:20:33,774 --> 00:20:35,317
<font color="yellow">- Selamat pagi.
- Pagi.</font>

253
00:20:37,194 --> 00:20:38,528
<font color="yellow">- Hei.
- Hai.</font>

254
00:20:41,365 --> 00:20:42,866
<font color="yellow">- Pagi.
- Pagi.</font>

255
00:20:43,034 --> 00:20:44,284
<font color="yellow">Pakaiannya masih lembab.</font>

256
00:20:44,452 --> 00:20:45,744
<font color="yellow">Matahari akan mengeringkannya nanti.</font>

257
00:20:45,912 --> 00:20:48,872
<font color="yellow">- Kau mencuci pakaianku?
- Itu terbaik yang bisa kami lakukan.</font>

258
00:20:49,040 --> 00:20:50,248
<font color="yellow">Mencuci dengan papan penggilasan...</font>

259
00:20:50,416 --> 00:20:52,500
<font color="yellow">...tidak sebersih dengan
mesin cuci di rumah.</font>

260
00:20:52,668 --> 00:20:54,586
<font color="yellow">Kau baik sekali.
Terima kasih.</font>

261
00:20:59,288 --> 00:21:00,425
<font color="yellow">Lihat mereka.</font>

262
00:21:00,593 --> 00:21:02,677
<font color="yellow">Burung pemakan bangkai.</font>

263
00:21:02,845 --> 00:21:04,721
<font color="yellow">Ya, habis hingga bersih.</font>

264
00:21:04,889 --> 00:21:06,640
<font color="yellow">Generator butuh setiap tetes
bahan bakar yang ada.</font>

265
00:21:06,807 --> 00:21:10,018
<font color="yellow">Tak akan ada listrik tanpa itu.
Maaf, Glenn.</font>

266
00:21:10,186 --> 00:21:12,938
<font color="yellow">Kupikir aku bisa mengendarainya
setidaknya beberapa hari lagi.</font>

267
00:21:13,105 --> 00:21:16,358
<font color="yellow">Mungkin kita harus mencuri
yang lain lagi suatu hari.</font>

268
00:21:21,530 --> 00:21:23,281
<font color="yellow">Selamat pagi, Petugas.</font>

269
00:21:23,449 --> 00:21:25,283
<font color="yellow">Hei.</font>

270
00:21:29,205 --> 00:21:30,997
<font color="yellow">Tidurmu nyenyak?</font>

271
00:21:32,041 --> 00:21:34,459
<font color="yellow">Sudah lama tak senyenyak itu.</font>

272
00:21:36,295 --> 00:21:39,839
<font color="yellow">Aku tak mau membangunkanmu.
Kupikir kau membutuhkannya.</font>

273
00:21:42,802 --> 00:21:45,470
<font color="yellow">- Astaga. Apa?
- Aku memikirkan...</font>

274
00:21:45,638 --> 00:21:47,931
<font color="yellow">...pria yang kami tinggalkan.</font>

275
00:21:51,102 --> 00:21:52,852
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak serius.</font>

276
00:21:54,733 --> 00:22:01,068
