http://rizaladam.wordpress.com</font>

277
00:22:01,654 --> 00:22:02,988
<font color="yellow">Air sudah datang, semuanya.</font>

278
00:22:03,155 --> 00:22:05,740
<font color="yellow">Jangan lupa merebusnya
sebelum memakainya.</font>

279
00:22:12,289 --> 00:22:14,833
<font color="yellow">Apa kau memintaku
atau memberitahuku?</font>

280
00:22:16,002 --> 00:22:17,836
<font color="yellow">- Meminta.
- Menurutku itu gila.</font>

281
00:22:18,004 --> 00:22:21,673
<font color="yellow">Kurasa itu cara paling
bodoh untuk menghancurkan...</font>

282
00:22:21,841 --> 00:22:23,133
<font color="yellow">- Ibu!
- Carl?</font>

283
00:22:23,300 --> 00:22:24,467
<font color="yellow">Di sana!</font>

284
00:22:24,635 --> 00:22:25,844
<font color="yellow">- Ayah!
- Sayang!</font>

285
00:22:26,012 --> 00:22:28,304
<font color="yellow">- Ibu!
- Rick!</font>

286
00:22:28,472 --> 00:22:30,348
<font color="yellow">- Carl!
- Ke arah sini. Ayo!</font>

287
00:22:30,516 --> 00:22:32,892
<font color="yellow">Carl! Sayang!</font>

288
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:35,020
<font color="yellow">- Ibu!
- Tak apa! Aku saja.</font>

289
00:22:35,187 --> 00:22:37,147
<font color="yellow">Tak ada yang menggigitmu?
Tak ada yang mencakarmu?</font>

290
00:22:37,314 --> 00:22:38,481
<font color="yellow">Tidak, aku tak apa.</font>

291
00:23:35,873 --> 00:23:37,916
<font color="yellow">Ini yang pertama kali
kami temukan di sini.</font>

292
00:23:38,084 --> 00:23:40,251
<font color="yellow">Mereka tak pernah datang
sejauh ini ke pegunungan.</font>

293
00:23:40,419 --> 00:23:43,004
<font color="yellow">Mereka kehabisan makanan
di kota, itulah sebabnya.</font>

294
00:24:05,361 --> 00:24:09,239
<font color="yellow">- Astaga.
- Brengsek.</font>

295
00:24:10,741 --> 00:24:12,742
<font color="yellow">Itu rusaku!</font>

296
00:24:14,829 --> 00:24:16,746
<font color="yellow">Lihat ini.
Sudah digigit oleh...</font>

297
00:24:16,914 --> 00:24:18,790
<font color="yellow">...bedebah kotor,
pembawa penyakit...</font>

298
00:24:18,958 --> 00:24:21,709
<font color="yellow">...bajingan yang tak punya ibu!</font>

299
00:24:21,877 --> 00:24:23,294
<font color="yellow">Tenanglah, Nak.
Itu tidak membantu.</font>

300
00:24:23,462 --> 00:24:24,963
<font color="yellow">Kau tahu apa, Pak Tua?</font>

301
00:24:25,131 --> 00:24:27,799
<font color="yellow">Kenapa tak lepas topi bodohmu itu
dan kembali nonton "On Golden Pond"?</font>

302
00:24:27,967 --> 00:24:31,636
<font color="yellow">Aku telah melacak rusa
ini dari jauh sekali.</font>

303
00:24:31,804 --> 00:24:33,638
<font color="yellow">Aku berencana membawanya
ke perkemahan...</font>

304
00:24:33,806 --> 00:24:35,765
<font color="yellow">...dan memasak daging rusa.</font>

305
00:24:35,933 --> 00:24:37,767
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana menurutmu?
Apakah kita bisa memotong...</font>

306
00:24:37,935 --> 00:24:39,310
<font color="yellow">...bagian yang sudah digigit ini?</font>

307
00:24:39,478 --> 00:24:40,937
<font color="yellow">Aku tak akan mengambil resiko.</font>

308
00:24:41,105 --> 00:24:43,606
<font color="yellow">Sayang sekali.</font>

309
00:24:43,774 --> 00:24:46,276
<font color="yellow">Aku bawa selusin tupai.</font>

310
00:24:46,443 --> 00:24:49,154
<font color="yellow">Itu harusnya cukup.</font>

311
00:24:53,617 --> 00:24:55,160
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan.</font>

312
00:24:56,912 --> 00:24:58,913
<font color="yellow">Ayolah, semuanya.
Apa-apaan ini?</font>

313
00:25:06,547 --> 00:25:08,339
<font color="yellow">Harus kena otaknya.</font>

314
00:25:08,507 --> 00:25:10,592
<font color="yellow">Apa kalian tak tahu
apa-apa?</font>

315
00:25:19,185 --> 00:25:20,518
<font color="yellow">Merle!</font>

316
00:25:22,354 --> 00:25:25,773
<font color="yellow">Merle! Kemarilah!</font>

317
00:25:26,942 --> 00:25:28,359
<font color="yellow">Kubawakan tupai untuk kita!</font>

318
00:25:28,527 --> 00:25:30,320
<font color="yellow">Mari kita rebus.</font>

319
00:25:31,697 --> 00:25:35,408
<font color="yellow">Daryl, tunggu dulu.
Aku perlu bicara padamu.</font>

320
00:25:38,037 --> 00:25:39,704
<font color="yellow">Tentang apa?</font>

321
00:25:39,872 --> 00:25:42,040
<font color="yellow">Tentang Merle.</font>

322
00:25:42,208 --> 00:25:43,666
<font color="yellow">Ada...</font>

323
00:25:43,834 --> 00:25:45,835
<font color="yellow">Ada masalah di Atlanta.</font>

324
00:25:53,761 --> 00:25:55,678
<font color="yellow">Dia mati?</font>

325
00:25:57,056 --> 00:25:59,098
<font color="yellow">Kami tidak yakin.</font>

326
00:25:59,266 --> 00:26:01,226
<font color="yellow">Entah dia sudah mati
atau belum!</font>

327
00:26:01,393 --> 00:26:03,895
<font color="yellow">Tak ada cara yang mudah,
jadi aku akan mengatakannya.</font>

328
00:26:04,980 --> 00:26:07,232
<font color="yellow">- Siapa kau?
- Rick Grimes.</font>

329
00:26:07,399 --> 00:26:10,818
<font color="yellow">Rick Grimes, ada yang ingin
kau sampaikan padaku?</font>

330
00:26:10,986 --> 00:26:12,904
<font color="yellow">Kakakmu membahayakan
kami semua...</font>

331
00:26:13,072 --> 00:26:16,032
<font color="yellow">...jadi aku memborgolnya di atap,
pada sepotong logam.</font>

332
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:18,326
<font color="yellow">Dia masih di sana.</font>

333
00:26:18,494 --> 00:26:22,080
<font color="yellow">Tunggu.
Biar kucerna dulu.</font>

334
00:26:22,248 --> 00:26:25,124
<font color="yellow">Kau bilang kau memborgol
kakakku di atap...</font>

335
00:26:25,292 --> 00:26:26,834
<font color="yellow">...dan kau meninggalkannya
di sana?</font>

336
00:26:27,002 --> 00:26:28,920
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

337
00:26:36,178 --> 00:26:37,595
<font color="yellow">Hati-hati dengan pisaunya!</font>

338
00:26:42,101 --> 00:26:43,893
<font color="yellow">Tak apa.</font>

339
00:26:44,061 --> 00:26:47,230
<font color="yellow">- Sebaiknya kau lepaskan aku!
- Kurasa lebih baik jika tidak.</font>

340
00:26:47,398 --> 00:26:49,357
<font color="yellow">Kuncian leher tidak sah.</font>

341
00:26:49,525 --> 00:26:51,192
<font color="yellow">Kau bisa ajukan keluhan.</font>

342
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:53,615
<font color="yellow">Ayolah, Kawan. Kita
bisa lakukan ini seharian.</font>

343
00:26:54,655 --> 00:26:57,282
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin berdiskusi dengan
tenang untuk masalah ini.</font>

344
00:26:57,449 --> 00:26:59,325
<font color="yellow">Menurutmu kita bisa
melakukannya?</font>

345
00:26:59,493 --> 00:27:02,662
<font color="yellow">Menurutmu kita bisa
melakukannya?</font>

346
00:27:03,831 --> 00:27:05,623
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

347
00:27:08,252 --> 00:27:10,628
<font color="yellow">Aku melakukannya bukan
tanpa alasan.</font>

348
00:27:10,796 --> 00:27:14,757
<font color="yellow">Kakakmu tak bekerja sama
dan tak akur dengan yang lainnya.</font>

349
00:27:14,925 --> 00:27:18,720
<font color="yellow">Itu bukan salah Rick.
Aku yang membawa kuncinya.</font>

350
00:27:18,887 --> 00:27:21,431
<font color="yellow">- Aku menjatuhkannya.
- Kau tak bisa memungutnya?</font>

351
00:27:21,598 --> 00:27:24,017
<font color="yellow">Aku menjatuhkannya
ke talang air.</font>

352
00:27:31,859 --> 00:27:34,027
<font color="yellow">Jika menurutmu itu membuatku
merasa lebih baik, itu tidak.</font>

353
00:27:34,194 --> 00:27:35,611
<font color="yellow">Mungkin ini akan
membuatmu lebih baik.</font>

354
00:27:35,779 --> 00:27:37,572
<font color="yellow">Aku merantai pintu
yang menuju ke atap...</font>

355
00:27:37,740 --> 00:27:39,324
<font color="yellow">...agar zombie tak bisa mendekatinya...</font>

356
00:27:39,491 --> 00:27:43,244
<font color="yellow">- ...dengan gembok.
- Hal itu patut diperhitungkan.</font>

357
00:27:48,876 --> 00:27:50,626
<font color="yellow">Persetan dengan kalian semua!</font>

358
00:27:50,794 --> 00:27:52,962
<font color="yellow">Beritahu saja aku
ada di mana dia...</font>

359
00:27:53,130 --> 00:27:55,006
<font color="yellow">...agar aku bisa menjemputnya.</font>

360
00:27:55,174 --> 00:27:57,633
<font color="yellow">Dia akan menunjukkannya padamu.</font>

361
00:27:57,801 --> 00:27:59,635
<font color="yellow">Bukankah begitu?</font>

362
00:28:05,976 --> 00:28:07,977
<font color="yellow">Aku akan kembali.</font>

363
00:28:25,037 --> 00:28:26,829
<font color="yellow">Jadi hanya itu?</font>

364
00:28:26,997 --> 00:28:28,831
<font color="yellow">Kau akan pergi begitu saja?</font>

365
00:28:28,999 --> 00:28:30,708
<font color="yellow">Persetan dengan semuanya?</font>

366
00:28:30,876 --> 00:28:32,627
<font color="yellow">Aku tak bilang begitu.</font>

