dengan pekerjaan kalian.</font>

543
00:39:21,026 --> 00:39:23,569
<font color="yellow">Ini bukan klub lawak.</font>

544
00:39:26,531 --> 00:39:28,323
<font color="yellow">Hei, Carl...</font>

545
00:39:28,491 --> 00:39:30,659
<font color="yellow">Ingat kata Ibu untuk terus
berada dalam pengawasan Dale?</font>

546
00:39:30,827 --> 00:39:33,245
<font color="yellow">Tapi Shane bilang kami bisa
menangkap katak, ingat?</font>

547
00:39:33,413 --> 00:39:35,289
<font color="yellow">Tak peduli apa kata Shane.
Yang penting adalah ucapan Ibu.</font>

548
00:39:35,457 --> 00:39:37,958
<font color="yellow">Kembalilah ke kemah.</font>

549
00:39:38,126 --> 00:39:40,127
<font color="yellow">Ibu akan menyusulmu.</font>

550
00:39:43,840 --> 00:39:45,549
<font color="yellow">Aku harus memberitahumu.</font>

551
00:39:45,717 --> 00:39:47,593
<font color="yellow">Kurasa kau tak seharusnya
melampiaskan itu padanya.</font>

552
00:39:47,761 --> 00:39:49,887
<font color="yellow">Jangan ajari aku.
Kau sudah tak punya hak untuk itu.</font>

553
00:39:50,055 --> 00:39:52,890
<font color="yellow">Lori, bisakah kau tunggu sebentar?
Kurasa kita harus bicara.</font>

554
00:39:53,058 --> 00:39:54,224
<font color="yellow">- Tak ada kesempatan itu.
- Tidak.</font>

555
00:39:54,392 --> 00:39:56,800
<font color="yellow">Itu juga sudah berakhir.
Katakan itu pada katak-katak itu.</font>

556
00:39:56,848 --> 00:39:58,145
<font color="yellow">Sial, Lori. Dengar, aku tak tahu
bagaimana kau melihatnya...</font>

557
00:39:58,313 --> 00:40:00,105
<font color="yellow">- ...atau apa pendapatmu...
- Bagaimana tampaknya? Maaf.</font>

558
00:40:00,273 --> 00:40:02,816
<font color="yellow">Apa ada wilayah abu-abu di sini?
Biar kuperjelas.</font>

559
00:40:02,984 --> 00:40:04,943
<font color="yellow">Menjauhlah dariku.
Menjauhlah dari putraku.</font>

560
00:40:05,111 --> 00:40:06,987
<font color="yellow">Jangan memandangnya.
Jangan bicara padanya.</font>

561
00:40:07,155 --> 00:40:09,740
<font color="yellow">Mulai sekarang, keluargaku
tak boleh kau dekati.</font>

562
00:40:12,077 --> 00:40:13,911
<font color="yellow">Lori, kurasa itu tak adil.</font>

563
00:40:14,079 --> 00:40:17,039
<font color="yellow">- Shane, diam. Jangan!
- Kurasa itu tidak...</font>

564
00:40:17,207 --> 00:40:20,584
<font color="yellow">Suamiku sudah kembali.
Dia masih hidup.</font>

565
00:40:20,752 --> 00:40:23,378
<font color="yellow">Dia sahabatku.</font>

566
00:40:23,546 --> 00:40:26,256
<font color="yellow">Kau pikir aku tak bahagia
akan hal itu?</font>

567
00:40:26,424 --> 00:40:28,425
<font color="yellow">Beraninya kau?
Untuk apa kau bahagia?</font>

568
00:40:28,593 --> 00:40:31,929
<font color="yellow">Kau yang bilang padaku
bahwa dia telah tewas.</font>

569
00:40:33,807 --> 00:40:35,891
<font color="yellow">Brengsek.</font>

570
00:41:03,086 --> 00:41:06,839
<font color="yellow">Sial.
Kau jelek sekali.</font>

571
00:41:32,448 --> 00:41:33,699
<font color="yellow">Ed, begini saja.</font>

572
00:41:33,867 --> 00:41:35,659
<font color="yellow">Jika kau tak suka
hasil cuciannya...</font>

573
00:41:35,827 --> 00:41:38,996
<font color="yellow">...kau boleh turun tangan dan
mengerjakannya sendiri. Ini.</font>

574
00:41:39,164 --> 00:41:41,832
<font color="yellow">Bukan pekerjaanku, Nona.</font>

575
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:44,001
<font color="yellow">- Andrea, jangan.
- Apa pekerjaanmu, Ed?</font>

576
00:41:44,169 --> 00:41:45,878
<font color="yellow">Duduk-duduk sambil merokok?</font>

577
00:41:46,045 --> 00:41:48,589
<font color="yellow">Yang pasti bukan mendengarkan
wanita bermulut lancang.</font>

578
00:41:48,756 --> 00:41:51,967
<font color="yellow">Begini saja.
Ayo.</font>

579
00:41:52,135 --> 00:41:54,136
<font color="yellow">Kurasa dia tak perlu pergi
ke mana pun bersamamu, Ed.</font>

580
00:41:54,304 --> 00:41:56,346
<font color="yellow">Aku bilang itu bukan urusanmu.
Ayo.</font>

581
00:41:56,514 --> 00:41:58,348
<font color="yellow">- Kau dengar aku.
- Carol.</font>

582
00:41:58,516 --> 00:42:00,517
<font color="yellow">Andrea, kumohon.
Itu tidak penting.</font>

583
00:42:00,685 --> 00:42:03,187
<font color="yellow">Jangan pikir aku tak bisa
menghajarmu...</font>

584
00:42:03,354 --> 00:42:05,022
<font color="yellow">...hanya karena kau terpelajar.</font>

585
00:42:05,190 --> 00:42:06,690
<font color="yellow">Mengerti?</font>

586
00:42:06,858 --> 00:42:09,359
<font color="yellow">Kau ikut sekarang atau
kau akan menyesalinya nanti.</font>

587
00:42:09,527 --> 00:42:11,695
<font color="yellow">Agar dia bisa muncul
dengan lebam baru, Ed?</font>

588
00:42:11,863 --> 00:42:13,697
<font color="yellow">Ya, kami pernah melihatnya.</font>

589
00:42:13,865 --> 00:42:15,908
<font color="yellow">Jangan ikut campur.
Ayo!</font>

590
00:42:16,075 --> 00:42:18,368
<font color="yellow">Kalian tahu?
Ini bukan urusan kalian.</font>

591
00:42:18,536 --> 00:42:20,996
<font color="yellow">Kalian jangan mencari
gara-gara.</font>

592
00:42:21,164 --> 00:42:23,540
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah cukup bicara.
Ayo.</font>

593
00:42:23,708 --> 00:42:25,834
<font color="yellow">Tidak. Carol, kau tak perlu...</font>

594
00:42:26,002 --> 00:42:28,337
<font color="yellow">Jangan perintah aku!
Aku yang akan memerintahmu!</font>

595
00:42:30,673 --> 00:42:32,591
<font color="yellow">- Kau pikir kau bisa...
- Lepaskan dia!</font>

596
00:42:32,759 --> 00:42:34,426
<font color="yellow">- Kemari!
- Lepaskan dia!</font>

597
00:42:34,594 --> 00:42:37,179
<font color="yellow">- Lepaskan dia!
- Lepaskan aku!</font>

598
00:42:39,170 --> 00:42:39,431
<font color="yellow">Ed?</font>

599
00:42:39,599 --> 00:42:41,725
<font color="yellow">- Tak apa-apa.
- Tidak!</font>

600
00:42:42,894 --> 00:42:44,353
<font color="yellow">- Tak apa-apa.
- Tidak!</font>

601
00:42:55,865 --> 00:42:57,866
<font color="yellow">Shane, hentikan!</font>

602
00:42:58,034 --> 00:42:59,451
<font color="yellow">Hentikan!</font>

603
00:43:00,620 --> 00:43:02,996
<font color="yellow">Hentikan!</font>

604
00:43:03,164 --> 00:43:04,998
<font color="yellow">- Hentikan!
- Jika kau memukul istri...</font>

605
00:43:05,166 --> 00:43:06,959
<font color="yellow">...anak perempuanmu atau
siapa pun di perkemahan ini...</font>

606
00:43:07,126 --> 00:43:09,336
<font color="yellow">...satu kali lagi, aku tak akan
berhenti lain kali. Kau dengar?</font>

607
00:43:09,504 --> 00:43:11,255
<font color="yellow">- Kau dengar aku?
- Ya.</font>

608
00:43:11,422 --> 00:43:13,131
<font color="yellow">- Akan kupukul kau sampai mati, Ed.
- Ed!</font>

609
00:43:13,299 --> 00:43:15,926
<font color="yellow">- Akan kupukul kau sampai mati.
- Ya Tuhan!</font>

610
00:43:16,094 --> 00:43:17,469
<font color="yellow">Tidak.</font>

611
00:43:17,637 --> 00:43:20,097
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan!</font>

612
00:43:21,307 --> 00:43:24,101
<font color="yellow">Ed, maafkan aku.</font>

613
00:43:24,269 --> 00:43:27,938
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan.
Ed, maafkan aku.</font>

614
00:43:29,065 --> 00:43:31,942
<font color="yellow">Aku sungguh minta maaf, Ed.</font>

615
00:43:32,110 --> 00:43:34,528
<font color="yellow">Ed, maafkan aku.</font>

616
00:43:34,696 --> 00:43:36,822
<font color="yellow">Maafkan aku, Ed.</font>

617
00:43:52,380 --> 00:43:55,507
<font color="yellow">Merle! Merle!</font>

618
00:44:01,848 --> 00:44:04,808
<font color="yellow">Tidak!</font>

619
